25|$|On 6 September 2012, Continental {{returned}} to the benchmark DAX index of 30 selected German blue chip stocks after a 45-month absence. Schaeffler AG is the <b>controlling</b> <b>shareholder</b> and currently owns 46% of Continental shares.|$|E
